sentences: Dragan Kojić (Serbo-Croatian Cyrillic: Драган Којић; born 7 October 1956), better known as Keba (Serbo-Croatian Cyrillic: Кеба), is a Serbian and former Yugoslavian singer.
Debuted in 1976, he has a career spanning more than four decades and remains one of the most acclaimed Serbian folk singers.
